posts.body:

>>3048f354-7eed-4786-9b80-6ddbbe4d43b1
I don't have all of them myself, but I'm willing to contribute. Finding time to do this is also hard.

The problem with Tor darknet is that all those lovingly crafted indexes disappear when the sites inevitably go down. ZeroNet can solve that.

For distribution of the files themselves the community here is too small, so just indexing it and maybe even post clearnet links to archives here? Maybe just onion links to the threads?
